    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3 in pristine condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp through individual throttle bodies with a razor-sharp throttle response. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential. Mechanically flawless, the dual-VANOS system has been proactively serviced, and the rear subframe has been reinforced to ensure structural integrity. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior retains its original deep luster, while the suspension geometry remains tight, offering the pure, communicative steering feel this chassis is renowned for. A meticulously maintained specimen for the discerning purist.",
