      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that presents exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that makes the paint pop. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather seats show absolutely no bolster wear, and the interior still retains that distinct factory-fresh scent. Every switch, dial, and electronic feature operates with tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been stored in a climate-controlled garage and maintained with an open-checkbook philosophy. All service records are meticulously organized and included. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade specimen for the most discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
